00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:13,110
By looking at her!

275
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:14,560
Take a look.

276
00:21:20,510 --> 00:21:22,270
What a perfect piece of work!

277
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:39,440
I came here with tribute and cash.

278
00:21:39,510 --> 00:21:41,000
I'll make up for what I owe.

279
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,270
I'll get to the bottom

280
00:21:46,350 --> 00:21:47,200
of what needs

281
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:48,790
