282
00:21:52,590 --> 00:21:54,160
Go back and tell Mr. Suphan.

283
00:21:55,350 --> 00:21:56,190
I, Ji Zhijie, will

284
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,480
make sure he gets the goods.

285
00:22:01,510 --> 00:22:02,350
And,

286
00:22:02,790 --> 00:22:03,630
