287
00:22:05,070 --> 00:22:06,880
Don't you dare to cause trouble

288
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,920
or hurt my people on my turf.

289
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:12,240
I'm still the same as before.

290
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,400
Do you understand?

291
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:17,480
Do you understand?

292
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:24,880
Assign more guards to Hao Yu.

293
00:22:25,310 --> 00:22:26,150
Yes.

294
00:22:47,830 --> 00:22:48,880
It was him, right?

295
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,240
Hao Yu.

296
00:22:50,790 --> 00:22:51,630
Hao Yu,

297
00:22:52,070 --> 00:22:53,110
don't accept anything

298
00:22:53,590 --> 00:22:54,790
from strangers lately.

299
00:22:55,030 --> 00:22:56,310
Don't pick up unknown calls,

300
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:57,640
and don't leave the house.

301
00:22:57,880 --> 00:22:58,720
Okay?

302
00:23:06,590 --> 00:23:07,880
Did you meet them?

303
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:12,270
Did they hurt you?

304
00:23:12,830 --> 00:23:14,440
He's working for Suphan, isn't he?

305
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:15,960
Don't worry.

306
00:23:16,750 --> 00:23:17,790
Don't worry. I'm here.

307
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:20,400
Everything is fine. Don't be afraid.

308
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:24,690
How about this?

309
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:26,200
I'll have Feilong take you to the UK first.

310
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:29,750
Bring Ling and Bei with you,

311
00:23:30,270 --> 00:23:31,160
so you won't get bored.

312
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:34,240
I'm not going anywhere.

313
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:36,680
We had a deal, remember?

314
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:38,790
We should face

315
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:39,880
everything together.

316
00:23:43,070 --> 00:23:43,910
But...

317
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:46,000
If it's my fault,

318
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:47,240
I'll go apologize.

319
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:48,350
If it helps you, I'll do it.

320
00:24:09,830 --> 00:24:10,670
Miss Hao Yu,

321
00:24:13,510 --> 00:24:14,960
there's no one I can't handle

322
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:17,510
in this world, except for you.

323
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:51,270
The real fear is they're setting a trap.

324
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:53,070
Even with all his skills,

325
00:24:53,270 --> 00:24:54,160
Zhijie may not find a way out.

326
00:24:55,070 --> 00:24:55,910
What if

327
00:24:57,550 --> 00:24:59,270
we send Hao Yu to Yingquan

328
